overview: Maitland Ward returns in her larger than life persona as Mistress Maitland, a mysterious femme fatale with a penchant for games. Relieved now of her husband, Ward looks back at the moments that made her who she is as she leads an audience through her journey from a curious submissive to a queen of dommes with a string of delegates and sexual destruction in her wake. Starring in each of these four perfectly formed scenes, Ward proves once again that she is a master at her craft.
title: Mistress Maitland 2
